    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I am absolutely thrilled to put this beauty up for sale. It\u2019s in total mint condition\u2014honestly, it looks and smells like it just left the showroom floor! I\u2019ve truly babied this car, keeping it garage-kept and spotless inside and out. It drives like an absolute dream, and I know the next owner is going to fall in love with it just like I did. If you're looking for perfection on wheels, you've found it! Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
