      "description": "We are pleased to present an exceptional vehicle that redefines the standards of the pre-owned market. This specimen remains in showroom condition, reflecting a history of meticulous stewardship and climate-controlled storage. Every surface, from the flawless exterior finish to the untouched interior upholstery, demonstrates an uncompromising commitment to preservation. Mechanically, the vehicle performs with the precision of a factory-fresh unit. For the discerning collector or enthusiast who demands nothing less than perfection, this offering represents an unrivaled opportunity.",
      "price": 48500.0,
