    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I\u2019m parting ways with my absolute pride and joy. This beauty is in truly stunning shape\u2014it\u2019s been pampered since day one and honestly looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor. No scratches, no spills, just pure perfection! I\u2019ve kept it garage-stored and followed every single maintenance check-up to a T. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically flawless and ready for its next adventure, you\u2019ve found it. Come take a look and see for yourself\u2014you\u2019re going to love it! \u2728",
      "price": 48500.0,
