    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in impeccable condition. This example features the high-revving S54B32 inline-six, utilizing individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing to deliver a linear power band up to an 8,000 RPM redline. The drivetrain is anchored by a Getrag 420G six-speed manual transmission and a limited-slip M-Variable Differential Lock. This chassis has received proactive subframe reinforcement and a comprehensive cooling system overhaul. The suspension maintains factory-spec geometry with refreshed bushings and dampers, ensuring the telepathic handling the E46 is renowned for. With original paint depth and a pristine interior, this is a mechanically flawless specimen for the discerning purist.",
